<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148924" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="15"><ahelp hid=".uno:FillShadow">Adds a shadow to the selected object. If the object already has a shadow, the shadow is removed. If you click this icon when no object is selected, the shadow is added to the next object that you draw.</ahelp></paragraph>
